00:45:18,327 --> 00:45:22,798
Craig was delighted to get so many
specimens lifted to the surface,

687
00:45:23,087 --> 00:45:25,726
even if they were less than fragrant.

688
00:45:26,287 --> 00:45:28,278
<i>They do smell pretty bad,</i>

